<heading>show - Show contact details.</heading>
<rule/>
<heading level="2">Usage</heading>
<pre>show NAME</pre>
<heading level="2">Description</heading>
<paragraph>Displays all details of a specific contact.</paragraph>
<heading level="2">Examples</heading>
<pre>show John
  Show details for John.</pre>
<heading level="2">See also</heading>
<paragraph>add, delete, edit, find, list</paragraph>
